ito-interno-para-a-melhoria-de-seus-padroes-/8357041|title=1\u00ba BATALH\u00c3O DE DEFESA QU\u00cdMICA, BIOL\u00d3GICA, RADIOL\u00d3GICA E NUCLEAR REALIZA CONCURSO DE ORDEM UNIDA NO \u00c2MBITO INTERNO PARA A MELHORIA DE SEUS PADR\u00d5ES.|website=eb.mil.br|date=7 May 2018|accessdate=17 April 2020}}</ref>\n*Radiological and Nuclear Defense Company - Special Operations Command (''Companhia de Defesa Qu\u00edmica, Biol\u00f3gica, Radiol\u00f3gica e Nuclear - Comando de Opera\u00e7\u00f5es Especiais'')<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.copesp.eb.mil.br/index.php/editoria-b/cia-dqbrn|title=COMPANHIA DE DEFESA QU\u00cdMICA, BIOL\u00d3GICA, RADIOL\u00d3GICA E NUCLEAR|website=copesp.eb.mil-br|date=|accessdate=17 April 2020}}</ref>\n[[Brazilian Navy|Navy]]\n*Nuclear, Biological, Chemical and Radiological Defense Center (''Centro de Defesa Nuclear, Biol\u00f3gica, Qu\u00edmica e Radiol\u00f3gica'')<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.marinha.mil.br/om/centro-de-defesa-nuclear-biologica-quimica-e-radiologica-da-mb|title=Centro de Defesa Nuclear, Biol\u00f3gica, Qu\u00edmica e Radiol\u00f3gica da MB|website=marinha.mil.br|date= |accessdate=17 April 2020}}</ref>\n** Nuclear, Biological, Chemical and Radiological Defense Battalion \u2013 Aramar Experimental Center (''Batalh\u00e3o de Defesa Nuclear, Biol\u00f3gica, Qu\u00edmica e Radiol\u00f3gica - Centro Experimental Aramar'')<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.marinha.mil.br/om/batalhao-de-defesa-nuclear-biologica-quimica-e-radiologica-de-aramar|title=Batalh\u00e3o de Defesa Nuclear, Biol\u00f3gica, Qu\u00edmica e Radiol\u00f3gica de Aramar|website=Marinha.mi.br|date=|accessdate=17 April 2020}}</ref>\n* Nuclear, Biological, Chemical and Radiological Defense Company \u2013 Naval Fusiliers Engineer Battalion (''Companhia de Defesa Nuclear, Biol\u00f3gica, Qu\u00edmica e Radiol\u00f3gica - Batalh\u00e3o de Engenharia de Fuzileiros Navais'')<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.defesanet.com.br/dqbrn/noticia/31362/Batalhao-de-Engenharia-de-Fuzileiro