.co/?idcategoria=411922|title=BATALL\u00d3N DE ATENCI\u00d3N Y PREVENCI\u00d3N DE DESASTRES NO. 80 \"BRIGADIER GENERAL \u00c1LVARO L\u00d3PEZ VARGAS\"|website=Ejercito.mil.co|date=|accessdate=17 April 2020}}</ref>\n** Nuclear, Biological and Chemical Company (''Compa\u00f1\u00eda Nuclear, Biol\u00f3gico y Qu\u00edmico'') <ref>{{cite web|url=https://ingenierosmilitaresdecolombia.wordpress.com/tag/nbq/|title=Capacidades del Batall\u00f3n de Atenci\u00f3n a Desastres al servicio de Colombia.|website=ingenierosmilitaresdecolombia|date=2 July 2013|accessdate=17 April 2020}}</ref>\n\n==Croatia==\n* Nuclear Biological and Chemical Defense Battalion (''Bojne Nuklearno-Biolo\u0161ko-Kemijske Obrane'') <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.morh.hr/bojna-nuklearno-biolosko-kemijske-obrane-hkov-a-sudjelovala-na-vjezbi-tim-1836-2018/|title=Bojna nuklearno-biolo\u0161ko-kemijske obrane HKoV-a sudjelovala na vje\u017ebi \u201cTIM 1836 \u2013 2018\u201d|website=morh.hr|date=12 April 2018 |accessdate=17 April 2020}}</ref>\n\n==Czech Republic==\n* 31st Radiological, Chemical and Biological Protection Regiment (''31. Pluk Radia\u010dn\u00ed, Chemick\u00e9 a Biologick\u00e9 Ochrany'') <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cbrn-liberec.army.cz/|title=31. pluk radia\u010dn\u00ed, chemick\u00e9 a biologick\u00e9 ochrany|website=cbrn-liberec.army.cz|date=|accessdate=17 April 2020}}</ref>\n** 311st Radiological, Chemical and Biological Protection Battalion (''311. Prapor Radia\u010dn\u00ed, Chemick\u00e9 a Biologick\u00e9 Ochrany'') <ref>{{cite web|url= https://www.armedconflicts.com/311th-Radiation-Chemical-and-Biological-Defense-Battalion-t63609|title=311. prapor radia\u010dn\u00ed, chemick\u00e9 a biologick\u00e9 ochrany|website=armedconflicts.com|date=|accessdate=17 April 2020}}</ref>\n**312th Radiological, Chemical and Biological Protection Battalion (''312. Prapor Radia\u010dn\u00ed, Chemick\u00e9 a Biologick\u00e9 Ochrany'') <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.armedconflicts.com/312th-Radiation-Chemi