c-abwehrkommando-der-bundeswehr/schule-abc-abwehr-und-gesetzliche-schutzaufgaben/|title=Schule ABC-Abwehr und Gesetzliche Schutzaufgaben|website=bundeswehr.de|date=|accessdate=17 April 2020}}</ref>\n\n==Hungary==\n* 93rd Chemical Protection Battalion \u201cS\u00e1ndor Pet\u0151fi\u201d (''MH 93. Pet\u0151fi S\u00e1ndor Vegyiv\u00e9delmi Z\u00e1szl\u00f3alj'') <ref>{{cite web|url=https://honvedelem.hu/alakulatok/mh-93-petofi-sandor-vegyivedelmi-zaszloalj-2/|title=MH 93. Pet\u0151fi S\u00e1ndor Vegyiv\u00e9delmi Z\u00e1szl\u00f3alj|website=honvedelem.hu|date=31 July 2012|accessdate=17 April 2020}}</ref>\n\n==India==\n[[Indian Army|Army]]\n*Faculty of Nuclear Biological Chemial Protection - College of Military Engineering<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3148632/ |title=Chemical, biological, radiological and nuclear training issues in India: A fresh perspective|author=Mudit Sharma|website=ncbi.nlm.nih.gov|date=|accessdate=17 April 2020}}</ref>\n[[Indian Air Force|Air Force]]\n* Air Force Institute of Nuclear Biological Chemical Protection<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bharat-rakshak.com/IAF/Database/Units/AFINBCP|title=Air Force Institute of NBC Protection|website=bharat-rakshak.com|date=|accessdate=17 April 2020}}</ref>\n\n==Indonesia==\n*Army Engineers Nuclear, Biological, and Chemical Company (''Kompi Zeni Nuklir, Biologi dan Kimia'') <ref>{{cite web|url=https://zeniad.wordpress.com/2009/01/21/detasmen-kompi-zeni-nubika-tni-ad-atau-detasmen-kompi-pengendali-senjata-pemusnah-massal/|title=KOMPI ZENI NUBIKA TNI AD\n |website=zeniad.wordpress.com|date=|accessdate=17 April 2020}}</ref>\n\n==Israel==\n* 76th Chemical Defense Battalion (''76 \u05d2\u05d3\u05d5\u05d3 \u05d4\u05e1\u05d9\u05d5\u05e2 \u05d4\u05db\u05d9\u05de\u05d9'') <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.handasa.org.il/print?c0=17700|title=\u05d2\u05d3\u05d5\u05d3 76|website=handasa.org.il|date=|accessdate=17 April 2020}}</ref>\n\n==Italy==\n* Joint Nuclear, Biological and Nuclear Defe